text: Fetor refers to an unpleasant odor emanating from an individual. Generally, a foul or unpleasant odor.Fetor in Miriam-Webster's Online Dictionary | http://medical.merriam-webster.com/medical/fetor Specific types include: * fetor oris, another term for halitosis * fetor hepaticus * uremic fetor * body odor * rectal fetor ==References== == External links == Category:Olfaction
title: Fetor
